    "description": "<p>CorpZap is the corporate services firm that knows your startup's needs better than you do. We work closely with founders and investors to help startups... well, start up.</p>\n<p>Within four years of launch, we have grown from relative obscurity to now service more than 800 international clients. Our depth of industry knowledge and experience in all stages of a startup's lifecycle makes us the top choice corporate services firm recommended by many investors, incubators, and accelerators in the region.</p>\n<p>At its core, CorpZap is also a technology startup that designs and builds its own automation software for the corporate services industry. &nbsp;This ensures that our services are scalable and always affordable for our clientele.</p>",
